textAnnotations.description:
"Munyard didn't tell me that. But I must confess
I'm relieved. But it still doesn't do
away
with the possibility of faulty design." He held
out his hand. "Maybe I will take a
: trip with
you
one of these days," he said. "In the meantime
I'll tell
editor that the story's a dead bird.
my
